  "steps": [
    "Heat oil and butter in a deep non-stick pan, add ginger, garlic and green chilli, mix and sauté till golden brown.",
    "Add onion, mix and sauté till translucent. Add cabbage, carrot, French beans, green peas, corn kernels, green capsicum and mushrooms, mix well and saute for 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add black pepper powder and salt and mix well. Add macaroni and vegetable stock and cook for 8-10 minutes or till macaroni is cooked.",
    "Transfer into a serving bowl and serve hot with lavash."
